overview: July 1st, 2007 :: Dragon Gate presents Kobe Pro-Wrestling Festival 2007. Matches include: •	Jack Evans and YAMATO vs Akira Tozawa and Taku Iwasa  •	Yuji Nagata vs "Hollywood" Stalker Ichikawa  •	Tetsuhiro Kuroda vs Don Fujii  •	Anthony W. Mori & Dragon Kid vs Gamma & Kinta Tamaoka  •	Yasushi Kanda vs Genki Horiguchi (c) for the Open The Brave Gate Championship •	RyoSuka (Susumu Yokosuka & Ryo Saito) vs Gedo & Jado (c) for the I-J Heavyweight Tag Team Championship •	Masaaki Mochizuki vs Koji Kanemoto  •	Muscle Outlaw'z (Magnitude Kishiwada, Masato Yoshino, and Naruki Doi) vs New Hazard (BxB Hulk, Cyber Kong, and Shingo Takagi) (c) for the Open The Triangle Gate Championship •	CIMA vs Jushin Thunder Liger (c) for the Open The Dream Gate Championship
title: DG Kobe Pro-Wrestling Festival 2007
